Description: Naruto, who wants to be a great ninja, must confront his inner demons at the Waterfall of Truth.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 53
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume, betrayals in the past, battles in the present.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 37
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Monkey D. Luffy and his motley crew of would-be pirates search for a legendary treasure called “One Piece.” In this volume, a familial tragedy.
Title: ONE PIECE, VOL. 59
Author: Eiichiro Oda

Description: This series is about grade-school boys who want to become professionals in the manga industry. In this installment, the boys struggle to rebound from cancellation.
Title: BAKUMAN, VOL. 8
Author: Tsugumi Ohba

Description: Rin Okumura joins an exorcist academy in order to control his inner demon. Will his classmates find out about his satanic bloodline?
Title: BLUE EXORCIST, VOL. 5
Author: Kazue Kato

Description: In this romantic comedy, Haruhi, a poor girl at a rich school, is forced to work — as a boy — for the school’s all-male club.
Title: OURAN HIGH SCHOOL HOST CLUB, VOL. 17
Author: Bisco Hatori

Description: These crime stories are set in a future (year 2030) version of Japan. Will the task force be able track down the serial killer and hacker "The Laughing Man"?
Title: GHOST IN THE SHELL: STAND ALONE COMPLEX, VOL. 2
Author: Yu Kinutani

Description: Meet Black Jack, a surgeon roaming the globe and performing medical miracles. Too bad he does not have a license to practice.
Title: BLACK JACK, VOL. 17
Author: Osamu Tezuka

Rank: Princess Nakaba and Prince Caesar are married to keep peace between warring countries. Will they learn to love each other?

Description: In "Shugo Chara," three guardians help an elementary school girl find her true self. In this series, the guardians take the spotlight.
Title: SHUGO CHARA CHAN, VOL. 1
Author: Peach-Pit
